          smallrule
"><div class="wsj-article-page-rule"></div></div><h3> <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/tampa-why-gen-z-and-millennial-tourists-are-flocking-to-this-retirement-mecca-1e2be027?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">坦帕：为什么 Z 世代和千禧一代游客涌向这个退休圣地</a></h3><h4>迈阿密？过去了。由于被这里的美食和酒吧以及步行便利性所吸引的年轻游客和居民涌入，这座沉睡的阳光地带城市正在迅速醒来。 <a href="https://www.wsj.com/articles/tampa-why-gen-z-and-millennial-tourists-are-flocking-to-this-retirement-mecca-1e2be027?mod=article_inline" target="_blank" class="icon none">读故事。</a> </h4><div class="media-object scope-
